movie_title: Star Wars: Episode IX - The Rise of Skywalker
title: GOOD FILM .....BUT NOT A GREAT FILM ....... 7/10 .
review: Gotta say i did enjoy this film but was expecting soooooo much more from the final film cos as a 46 year old bloke i have been waiting for this since my childhood , when the force awakens came out i fort yes here we go what a great film 8/10 they are going to smash this final trilogy then when the last jedi came out i fort oh dear that was poor 4/10 so i really wanted rise of skywalker to fix it and make a brilliant ending but was left wanting ahh well still an ok film tho 7/10 .
